xercises public `getTransactionManager()`, `register(...)`, and `unregister(...)`.\\n  - Uses real Bitronix classes so `DefaultTransactionManagerLookup` reaches:\\n    - `ClassLoader#loadClass(...)`\\n    - `Class#getMethod(...)`\\n    - `Method#invoke(...)`\\n    - for both Bitronix register and unregister paths.\\n  - Includes a minimal test `EhcacheXAResource` implementation in the test package.\\n  - Shuts down the Bitronix transaction manager and unregisters resources in cleanup.\\n\\nI did not compile or run tests, per workflow instructions.\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0189e448c894a1b1016a424c47ce6c819786540b45ef550677\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"oca/gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 360, \"output\": 1270, \"cacheRead\": 34816, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 36446, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1782729779746, \"responseId\": \"resp_0189e448c894a1b1016a424c3439d48197a99c8bfd3064ed77\"}, \"toolResults\": []}\n[recv] agent_end\n[send] get_state\n[recv] get_state success\n  sessionFile: ../../../../../../../../.pi/agent/sessions/--home-vjovanov-c-forge-forge3-graalvm-reachability-metadata-forge-local_repositories-forge_worktrees-2904-14b6c8f8--/2026-06-29T10-39-34-549Z_019f12f6-8895-73f9-9d85-6ef40aee1c73.jsonl\n  sessionId: 019f12f6-8895-73f9-9d85-6ef40aee1c73\n[send] get_session_stats\n[recv] get_session_stats success\n  tokens: input=66304 output=8241 cacheRead=601600 cacheWrite=0 total=676145\n\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
